[Episode 29]

4
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,070
Let me tell you a joke.

5
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:48,070
There was a scholar

6
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:50,960
who really loved braised ox heads.

7
00:01:51,550 --> 00:01:53,830
He could finish a whole head in one sitting.

8
00:01:53,830 --> 00:01:54,630
One day,

9
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,110
he had a dream.

10
00:01:57,030 --> 00:01:58,490
In this dream, he was dead.

11
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:01,080
An officer from the Underworld

12
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:02,450
came to bring him back.

13
00:02:02,830 --> 00:02:03,710
Seeing the officer,

14
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,630
the scholar

15
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:06,790
wasn't afraid at all.

16
00:02:07,630 --> 00:02:08,870
He even smiled at him.

17
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:12,230
Do you know why?

18
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:13,850
Because...

19
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:14,350
Because...

20
00:02:14,350 --> 00:02:16,880
Because the officer who came was the Ox-head.

21
00:02:18,070 --> 00:02:19,329
Have you heard of this?

22
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:21,270
I heard this joke

23
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,829
when I was seven or eight.

24
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:25,440
Aren't you too old-fashioned?

25
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:30,010
I have another one.

26
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,430
A tiger was living

27
00:02:37,510 --> 00:02:38,470
in the forest.

28
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:40,530
It often...

29
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:41,480
Gao Bingzhu,

30
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,990
I know you're afraid that I'd sleep

31
00:02:45,990 --> 00:02:46,990
and never wake up.

32
00:02:50,990 --> 00:02:51,720
Don't worry.

33
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:55,350
I won't give up.

34
00:02:59,310 --> 00:02:59,970
I trust you.

35
00:03:01,070 --> 00:03:02,030
I know you can.

36
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:05,410
Should we chat for a while?

37
00:03:07,510 --> 00:03:08,110
You see,

38
00:03:08,230 --> 00:03:09,960
I've always been curious about

39
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:13,430
how you became an interior guard

40
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:16,150
as a woman.

41
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:22,050
My brother is the leader of the Services.

42
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:23,470
All I needed

43
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:25,670
was his approval.

44
00:04:08,230 --> 00:04:08,630
Siyue,

45
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:10,040
show some mercy.

46
00:04:37,230 --> 00:04:38,630
You can't even win a fight

47
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,560
against a woman!

48
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,909
How do you protect Luoyang

49
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,320
and Her Majesty?

50
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,510
Practice more!

51
00:04:45,990 --> 00:04:46,670
Yes, sir!

52
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,630
From this moment,

53
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:56,909
Wu Siyue will officially become an interior guard.

54
00:04:56,909 --> 00:04:58,550
Address her

55
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:01,070
as 'Madam.'

56
00:05:04,150 --> 00:05:06,070
Madam!

57
00:05:11,110 --> 00:05:12,310
I almost hit Madam Wu

58
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:13,710
during the combat.

59
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,550
Madam.

60
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,390
Luckily, I was quick on my feet.

61
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:18,270
I pretended to be attacked and fell,

62
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,670
or Sir Wu must punish me

63
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:20,680
for hurting her.

64
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:22,490
What Madam?

65
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:23,930
She is just a woman.

66
00:05:24,350 --> 00:05:24,990
If Sir Wu hadn't asked us

67
00:05:24,990 --> 00:05:25,920
to go easy on her,

68
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:27,030
I would've defeated her ten times!

69
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:27,490
Enough.

70
00:05:28,110 --> 00:05:29,570
She is the sister of Sir Wu.

71
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,280
She joined the Services

72
00:05:31,470 --> 00:05:32,230
