85
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:52,990
One day,

86
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,300
you'll become a wife and a mother.

87
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:55,310
You can't put yourself

88
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,750
in danger every day!

89
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:02,310
If Beiqi competes with you seriously,

90
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,640
you won't have a chance.

91
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:30,350
How dare you!

92
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:34,270
Are you happy now?

93
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:44,590
I'm not as good as them.

94
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:45,590
I won't complain.

95
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:46,710
Next time,

96
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:49,720
we'll have serious combat.

97
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:56,070
So, you were angry

98
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:57,720
because they didn't

99
00:06:57,830 --> 00:06:59,270
take you seriously.

100
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:05,360
I was angry 'cause they were right.

101
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:08,470
I joined the Services

102
00:07:08,470 --> 00:07:09,350
