175
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,440
mother said that

176
00:09:57,470 --> 00:09:59,390
we can't eat until she's back.

177
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:00,450
Never mind.

178
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:02,660
I'll add some water to the congee.

179
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:03,720
