191
00:10:20,590 --> 00:10:21,230
Mother!

192
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:24,190
Mother!

193
00:10:24,470 --> 00:10:25,390
Mother!

194
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:26,560
Are you alright?

195
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:28,870
How dare you run away!

196
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,870
Hare dare you!

197
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:30,950
Mother, I'm sorry.

198
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:32,030
Mother, I'm so sorry.

199
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:32,760
How dare you!

200
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:34,950
You're sorry?

201
00:10:35,190 --> 00:10:36,050
