220
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:19,590
Please save my sister!

221
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:20,920
I will pay you later.

222
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:21,660
Please save my sister.

223
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:22,630
