224
00:11:22,630 --> 00:11:23,430
Bingzhu,

225
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:25,390
I'm not sick.

226
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,630
Let's go home.

227
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:27,810
It's alright, Tan.

228
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:29,020
Leave now.

229
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:30,390
Please, save my sister!

230
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:31,300
I promise.

231
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,510
I'll pay you in the future.

232
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:32,910
Let go.

233
00:11:32,990 --> 00:11:33,630
I'll do anything.

234
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:34,890
