252
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:17,400
Let's go.

253
00:12:18,990 --> 00:12:19,510
Tan

254
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:22,520
is seven years younger than me.

255
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:28,470
When I was exiled
from the Unwelcome Well 5 years ago,

256
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,670
