they almost started a fight with me.

602
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:47,230
He should be alright

603
00:27:47,230 --> 00:27:48,670
considering what you said.

604
00:27:48,670 --> 00:27:50,270
What worries me the most

605
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:51,190
is another thing.

606
00:27:51,190 --> 00:27:52,350
What thing?

607
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,590
My lord, where are you going?

608
00:27:55,590 --> 00:27:55,920
Home.

609
00:27:58,130 --> 00:28:02,660
[Baili Mansion]

610
00:28:00,470 --> 00:28:02,470
This is something we never mention.

611
00:28:03,230 --> 00:28:05,560
Master Baili Hu never let me talk about it.

612
00:28:05,870 --> 00:28:08,000
He was exiled from Four Season Academy

613
00:28:08,150 --> 00:28:09,750
because of argument.

614
00:28:10,390 --> 00:28:11,510
After he left,

615
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:14,070
horrible rumors were going around.

616
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:15,270
No one in the family

617
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:17,190
wanted him to be mistreated like this.

618
00:28:17,190 --> 00:28:18,390
So, the Baili family

619
00:28:18,670 --> 00:28:19,590
left Chang'an

620
00:28:19,830 --> 00:28:21,030
and moved to Luoyang.

621
00:28:21,990 --> 00:28:23,050
Why did they argue?

622
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:25,560
I have no idea

623
00:28:25,870 --> 00:28:26,830
what happened.

624
00:28:29,070 --> 00:28:30,070
You mentioned that

625
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:30,550
there were

626
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,990
horrible rumors about him.

627
00:28:31,990 --> 00:28:33,030
What rumors?

628
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:37,590
They said he performed witchcraft.

629
00:28:38,380 --> 00:28:38,910
However,

630
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:40,830
it reminds me that

631
00:28:40,900 --> 00:28:42,380
there was a time

632
00:28:42,750 --> 00:28:44,710
when the mansion was full of smoke

633
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:46,750
and pungent smell

634
00:28:46,950 --> 00:28:48,950
like what happened when you made elixirs.

635
00:28:48,950 --> 00:28:50,550
That's why people said

636
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:52,440
he knew witchcraft.

637
00:28:53,470 --> 00:28:54,670
When did that happen?

638
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:57,070
One year before we came to Luoyang.

639
00:28:57,670 --> 00:28:59,070
The 3rd year of Zhenlong.

640
00:28:59,350 --> 00:28:59,810
My lord!

641
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:01,570
My lord!

642
00:29:02,950 --> 00:29:03,680
Uncle Baili.

643
00:29:03,910 --> 00:29:04,370
My lord,

644
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,160
Gao Bingzhu is here.

645
00:29:12,070 --> 00:29:12,730
As you said,

646
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:14,790
those copper boxes

647
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,620
were full of imperfect Thunders.

648
00:29:16,620 --> 00:29:17,510
That's what

649
00:29:17,510 --> 00:29:18,770
Taoist Tiantong said.

650
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:35,040
The proportion is correct.

651
00:29:35,430 --> 00:29:36,310
This sword is heavy.

652
00:29:36,310 --> 00:29:38,310
It's made of copper from Mount Lian.

653
00:29:40,430 --> 00:29:41,190
It turns out that

654
00:29:41,190 --> 00:29:43,120
this is what the cooper is used for.

655
00:29:45,140 --> 00:29:46,190
[Guanglin Inn]

656
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:47,070
I've always thought

657
00:29:47,070 --> 00:29:47,990
that Four Season Clan

658
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:49,390
was making some elixirs.

659
00:29:49,710 --> 00:29:50,770
While I was testing

660
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:52,230
Tiantong's manuscript,

661
00:29:52,230 --> 00:29:54,430
I tried all the ingredients, formulas,

662
00:29:54,710 --> 00:29:55,910
and all types of woods

663
00:29:56,340 --> 00:29:58,470
to make sure the elixirs were perfect.

664
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:01,870
I took those small explosions

665
00:30:01,870 --> 00:30:03,110
as failures.

666
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:04,470
Now I see,

667
00:30:05,030 --> 00:30:06,830
that's what they're aiming for.

668
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:08,550
They don't want to

669
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:10,350
remove the toxicity of elixirs.

670
00:30:10,710 --> 00:30:12,640
They want Thunder, the explosive!

671
00:30:14,910 --> 00:30:16,630
They stole from those copper mines

672
00:30:16,630 --> 00:30:17,830
not to make fake coins

673
00:30:18,110 --> 00:30:19,350
or weapons,

674
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:21,470
but to make copper boxes.

675
00:30:24,070 --> 00:30:26,230
This type of copper has great hardness.

676
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:27,990
Once a Thunder explodes inside,

677
00:30:27,990 --> 00:30:29,070
the shattered pieces

678
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:30,270
will largely increase

679
00:30:30,270 --> 00:30:32,270
the explosion's radius and damage.

680
00:30:37,670 --> 00:30:38,510
What we saw

681
00:30:38,710 --> 00:30:40,030
was only an imperfect product.

682
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:41,760
It already caused a landslide.

683
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:43,230
If they succeed,

684
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:45,790
its damage will be beyond imagination.

685
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:51,080
I think they've already succeeded by now.

686
00:30:51,910 --> 00:30:53,110
Before you came here,

687
00:30:53,910 --> 00:30:55,590
I was forced to test the formula.

688
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,920
But while I was doing so,

689
00:30:57,150 --> 00:30:58,610
they found out the secret.

690
00:31:01,910 --> 00:31:02,440
I thought

691
00:31:02,590 --> 00:31:03,910
I could use frozen Xuanwu's Pearl

692
00:31:03,910 --> 00:31:06,310
to lower the temperature and buy more time.

693
00:31:06,390 --> 00:31:08,990
I didn't realize that it was this idea

694
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,470
that helped the furnace
to reach the right temperature.

695
00:31:10,470 --> 00:31:11,950
That's the key to success.

696
00:31:12,430 --> 00:31:13,490
Using this method,

697
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:14,150
they won't have

698
00:31:14,150 --> 00:31:15,530
useless ashes,

699
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:17,440
but Thunders that can be set off

700
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:18,310
at any time.

701
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:20,710
Do you mean

702
00:31:21,910 --> 00:31:22,910
you helped them

703
00:31:22,990 --> 00:31:24,230
solve the key issue

704
00:31:24,430 --> 00:31:25,690
of making the Thunder?

705
00:31:34,150 --> 00:31:35,810
Don't mention this to anyone.

706
00:31:36,030 --> 00:31:38,630
I have to report to
the Intelligence Services.

707
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:40,000
Gao Bingzhu,

708
00:31:46,670 --> 00:31:47,510
I didn't do it

709
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,440
intentionally,

710
00:31:48,830 --> 00:31:50,030
but this was my fault.

711
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:51,870
I'll take full responsibility

712
00:31:51,870 --> 00:31:52,670
for what I did.

713
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:57,950
You were in danger.

714
00:31:58,190 --> 00:31:59,250
It was an accident.

715
00:31:59,390 --> 00:32:00,590
It wasn't your fault.

716
00:32:00,670 --> 00:32:01,780
Without you,

717
00:32:02,430 --> 00:32:03,190
they would still

718
00:32:03,190 --> 00:32:03,990
succeed.

719
00:32:05,510 --> 00:32:06,570
You're the victim.

720
00:32:06,750 --> 00:32:07,630
Don't blame yourself

721
00:32:07,630 --> 00:32:08,590
for everything.

722
00:32:09,270 --> 00:32:09,950
Instead of

723
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:11,090
blaming yourself,

724
00:32:12,230 --> 00:32:13,890
why not think of ways to fix it?

725
00:32:25,390 --> 00:32:26,350
It's my fault.

726
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,110
I got carried away

727
00:32:29,470 --> 00:32:31,600
and told others about the manuscript,

728
00:32:31,870 --> 00:32:33,230
putting you and Hongyi

729
00:32:34,070 --> 00:32:35,990
in extreme danger.

730
00:32:36,190 --> 00:32:36,790
Father,

731
00:32:37,150 --> 00:32:38,590
we're alright now.

732
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:40,390
We returned home safely.

733
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:44,480
If anything had happened to you two...

734
00:32:45,670 --> 00:32:46,830
It's all my fault!

735
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:47,710
Father,

736
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:49,610
don't blame yourself.

737
00:32:49,990 --> 00:32:51,870
Taoist Tiantong is devious and cunning.

738
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:53,030
Even if you hadn't mentioned it,

739
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:54,390
he would have found us.

740
00:33:00,630 --> 00:33:01,110
Father,

741
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:03,240
have you met Liu Feng recently?

742
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:04,370
How is he doing?

743
00:33:09,070 --> 00:33:12,000
I'm afraid we will argue with each other
once we meet.

744
00:33:12,070 --> 00:33:13,430
I asked someone to go to

745
00:33:13,630 --> 00:33:15,630
Hong Xiao Fang to inquire about him.

746
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:18,950
He was kicked out

747
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:21,150
after he spent all his money.

748
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:25,990
Liu Feng is stubborn.

749
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:28,190
He was humiliated like this.

750
00:33:29,070 --> 00:33:30,670
I wonder if he can get over it.

751
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:33,270
I don't want him to sleep on the streets.

752
00:33:33,790 --> 00:33:35,650
I already sent people to find him.

753
00:33:35,990 --> 00:33:37,550
I finally realized that

754
00:33:38,550 --> 00:33:40,110
I should be blamed

755
00:33:40,630 --> 00:33:42,830
for everything that has ever happened.

756
00:33:43,630 --> 00:33:44,090
Father!

757
00:33:44,230 --> 00:33:44,910
I will never

758
00:33:45,270 --> 00:33:46,230
poke my nose

759
00:33:46,420 --> 00:33:47,680
into anything he does.

760
00:33:48,510 --> 00:33:50,110
He can marry whoever he likes

761
00:33:50,350 --> 00:33:52,070
and do whatever he wants.

762
00:33:53,430 --> 00:33:55,230
All I wish for is that

763
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:58,500
Hongyi and you can be safe and sound.

764
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:00,590
Father.

765
00:34:01,750 --> 00:34:02,210
My lady!

766
00:34:02,910 --> 00:34:03,390
My lady!

767
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:07,390
Uncle Baili, what happened?

768
00:34:07,750 --> 00:34:08,409
Lord Hongyi

769
00:34:08,830 --> 00:34:09,630
has gone mad!

770
00:34:10,429 --> 00:34:12,429
He wants to dig his brother's grave.

771
00:34:13,350 --> 00:34:13,989
In the following 15 days,

772
00:34:13,989 --> 00:34:15,510
all the entrances to Luoyang,

773
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,710
no matter for boats or carriages,

774
00:34:16,710 --> 00:34:17,590
should be examined closely

775
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:19,050
for anything suspicious.

776
00:34:20,030 --> 00:34:21,110
Contact all the middlemen

777
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:21,949
and field agents.

778
00:34:21,949 --> 00:34:22,909
If they see any copper boxes

779
00:34:22,909 --> 00:34:23,670
in the city,

780
00:34:23,949 --> 00:34:25,409
report to us immediately!

781
00:34:26,670 --> 00:34:27,030
Here.

782
00:34:27,179 --> 00:34:27,710
This one.

783
00:34:27,870 --> 00:34:28,199
Move.

784
00:34:48,030 --> 00:34:48,760
Gao Bingzhu!

785
00:34:51,270 --> 00:34:52,350
Gao Bingzhu!

786
00:34:52,429 --> 00:34:53,159
Gao Bingzhu!

787
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:08,280
Gao Bingzhu!

788
00:35:09,350 --> 00:35:10,080
Gao Bingzhu!

789
00:35:25,270 --> 00:35:25,710
Madam!

790
00:35:26,790 --> 00:35:27,750
Madam, are you alright?

791
00:35:27,750 --> 00:35:28,750
Why did you get up?

792
00:35:29,630 --> 00:35:30,750
Where is Gao Bingzhu?

793
00:35:30,750 --> 00:35:31,410
Where is he?

794
00:35:33,750 --> 00:35:34,550
Where?

795
00:35:35,190 --> 00:35:36,510
We were in a grave situation that day.

796
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:37,570
After we found you,

797
00:35:37,750 --> 00:35:39,610
we immediately brought you back.

798
00:35:39,790 --> 00:35:41,030
We didn't pay attention.

799
00:35:41,030 --> 00:35:41,510
Indeed.

800
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:43,550
Gao Bingzhu.

801
00:35:43,990 --> 00:35:44,520
Li Beiqi.

802
00:35:44,910 --> 00:35:46,110
I want to see Li Beiqi.

803
00:35:46,670 --> 00:35:47,800
We didn't see Sir Li.

804
00:35:48,070 --> 00:35:49,790
He probably went out.

805
00:35:50,550 --> 00:35:51,150
Tell him to see me

806
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:52,080
after he's back.

807
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:52,510
Yes.

808
00:35:52,830 --> 00:35:53,290
We will.

809
00:35:56,350 --> 00:35:57,610
Madam, have a rest now.

810
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:00,230
Your medicine is here.

811
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:03,300
[Li Chun, Interior Guard]

812
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:01,910
If you don't have other orders,

813
00:36:01,910 --> 00:36:02,630
I'll bring the medicine

814
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:03,430
to Sir Wu now.

815
00:36:05,470 --> 00:36:06,670
What happened to him?

816
00:36:13,030 --> 00:36:13,430
Sir,

817
00:36:13,790 --> 00:36:15,270
we confirmed with the Customs Office.

818
00:36:15,270 --> 00:36:16,310
Nobody saw the copper box

819
00:36:16,310 --> 00:36:17,510
Gao Bingzhu mentioned.

820
00:36:17,510 --> 00:36:18,510
Nothing has been reported

821
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:19,770
from those entrances.

822
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:21,400
In this case,

823
00:36:22,310 --> 00:36:23,190
Four Season Clan

824
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,510
hasn't transported

825
00:36:24,830 --> 00:36:27,490
a large number of Thunders
they made to Luoyang.

826
00:36:28,420 --> 00:36:29,150
We haven't received

827
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:30,710
any related news.

828
00:36:32,070 --> 00:36:32,990
Could the Thunder

829
00:36:32,990 --> 00:36:35,310
really cause such huge damage as you described?

830
00:36:35,310 --> 00:36:36,440
I saw it with my eyes.

831
00:36:36,950 --> 00:36:37,830
The Thunder

832
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:40,230
caused a landslide in the North Mountain.

833
00:36:40,230 --> 00:36:41,510
It was just a defective product

834
00:36:41,510 --> 00:36:42,770
discarded by the Clan.

835
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:45,070
If they improve the formula,

836
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:47,910
I can't imagine how powerful it will be.

837
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:49,030
In your opinion,

838
00:36:49,390 --> 00:36:50,230
why did

839
00:36:50,270 --> 00:36:51,950
Four Season Clan

840
00:36:52,990 --> 00:36:54,590
make such a powerful weapon?

841
00:36:57,790 --> 00:36:58,350
The Ceremony of Light.
